name: PROPERTIES 02 - Coffee in Little Nostalgia
description:
The following NFT corresponds to the collection of properties located in Kitty City in the Little Nostalgia neighborhood. 
This chic caffee is located 15 meters away from the central square of Little Nostalgia, it is considered the most famous petfriendly cafe in the city for its luxurious gourmet dishes for pets. 
Its construction of more than 70 years gives it a unique charm for tourists who want to relax with a cup of hot latte. 
Land measurements: 60m x 50m
